entries.s_11: Not at all. I have returned from the Rori crash site and I have a crate of supplies.
entries.s_13: Fantastic! I had received a report that the supplies wouldn't be making it. You just saved the Empire a great deal of money. Please hand me the supplies.
entries.s_15: Again?  You are truly the saviour.  I will be reporting your name to High Command! For once I get to report something positive. Please hand me the supplies.
entries.s_17: Looks like you have an inventory full of supplies you need to craft into a supply crate for me. Come back when that is done.
entries.s_18: Sorry, I don't have time to talk. Speak with Major Tantor if you have questions.
entries.s_5: I have very important business to attend to. Please speak with the Major if you have questions.
entries.s_9: Is this some sort of prank?
